Message.message: PRESS ACTION ONCE AND ONE DIRECTION TO DRAW A BOT THAT WILL MOVE IN THAT DIRECTION.
PRESS ACTION AT THE GREEN PLAY BUTTON TO START THE GAME!
PRESS ACTION TWICE AND AND ANY NUMBER OF DIRECTIONS TO DRAW A BOX.
PRESS ACTION ON ANY ALREADY DRAWN ITEM TO DELETE IT
PRESS ACTION AND LEFT OR RIGHT ON THE SLIDER ON THE BOTTOM TO CHANGE THE SIMULATION SPEED
BOXES CAN BE USED TO BRIDGE GAPS.
PLEASE DO NOT DROP BOTS OR THE BALL INTO THE GAP. THEY ARE HARD TO RETRIEVE.
